  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an adventure in the heights of the city and experience the unimaginable! Sickway brings realistic experiences and adventures which you wouldn't dare to try in real life. During your ride on a two wheeled electric vehicle, you will have to overcome obstacles, minigames and the biggest fear of all: fear of heights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MINIGAMES</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers thrilling minigames on which you will encounter multiple times during your exploring. Not only do they add fun to the game, but they also help you achieve your best possible time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRACK EDITOR</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is where creativity knows no boundaries. You can create your own tracks according to your imagination, change the environment or an atmosphere. On top of this you can share what you made to your friends and other players through steamworkshop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This mode is for up to 4 players, where fun meets competitiveness. By driving fast, the players race eachother and compete for the best results. You can choose from up to 5 different tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Availability</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- recommended VR sets: Meta Quest 2, HTC Vive sets, Meta Quest 3, Valve Index</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- playable VR sets: Oculus Rift, Pico 4</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extra Features</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- High-resolution VR game in a realistic city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic physics - the game is built on an advanced physics engine that guarantees realistic movements and interactions. You'll feel every step, every balance, and every impact or fall as if you were really there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- IRL falling (150m height)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Authentic experience - thanks to the environment and the physics model, you wll feel as if you are truly walking on narrow bridges high above the ground. Looking down will definitely get your adrenaline pumping. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Scenic views - enjoy interesting panoramic views of the cityscape.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an adventure in the heights of the city and experience the unimaginable! Sickway brings realistic experiences and adventures which you wouldn't dare to try in real life. During your ride on a two wheeled electric vehicle, you will have to overcome obstacles, minigames and the biggest fear of all: fear of heights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/fa09f396520019af24bde3631092844e.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MINIGAMES</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers thrilling minigames on which you will encounter multiple times during your exploring. Not only do they add fun to the game, but they also help you achieve your best possible time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/38c7044e1bcfcb5eaa50d3210ac51b45.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRACK EDITOR</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is where creativity knows no boundaries. You can create your own tracks according to your imagination, change the environment or an atmosphere. On top of this you can share what you made to your friends and other players through steamworkshop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/01746b41d2f2bb322032d860424a40bb.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This mode is for up to 4 players, where fun meets competitiveness. By driving fast, the players race eachother and compete for the best results. You can choose from up to 5 different tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.poster.avif?t=1736947155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.webm?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012470/extras/e47ba85fdda1176af0c8bab688d1493e.mp4?t=1736947155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Availability</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- recommended VR sets: Meta Quest 2, HTC Vive sets, Meta Quest 3, Valve Index</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- playable VR sets: Oculus Rift, Pico 4</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extra Features</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- High-resolution VR game in a realistic city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic physics - the game is built on an advanced physics engine that guarantees realistic movements and interactions. You'll feel every step, every balance, and every impact or fall as if you were really there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- IRL falling (150m height)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Authentic experience - thanks to the environment and the physics model, you wll feel as if you are truly walking on narrow bridges high above the ground. Looking down will definitely get your adrenaline pumping. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Scenic views - enjoy interesting panoramic views of the cityscape.</p>",
